Name: Go Run a Dungeon
About the game: About this game Run your dungeon as 4 different classes - Slash and smash incoming adventurers as a warrior. - Make use of the souls of the dead as a necromancer. - Harvest nature and the elements as an elementalist. - Make smart and tactical decisions as a tactician. Recruit different types of monster and creatures to fight for you - Support units will help you keep your dungeon running, providing you with income and mana. Goblins mostly fill this role. - Orcs, demons, slimes and more will fight for you, defending your dungeon from curious adventurers who venture too close. Encounter different events - Things are never dull when you are running a dungeon. Different people will pass by and events might happen. It could be the local village paying tribute to you out of fear, or a butch of fearless adventurers knocking on your door.
